meta {
  name: Tenant Isolation (404)
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{token}}
}

docs {
  # Tenant Isolation → 404

  **Pre-requisites:**
  1. Run "Get JWT Token" (tenant-001) and submit a payment to get a `paymentId`
  2. Run "Get Token (Tenant B)" (tenant-002) to switch to a different tenant
  3. Run this request — Tenant B cannot see Tenant A's payment

  **Expected:** 404 Not Found (no information leakage about whether the payment exists)
}

